      "source": "[36氪｜前米哈游高管创业，AI原生增长Agent LeapMind Growth获CMC资本领投](https://eu.36kr.com/zh/p/3786123369094405)；[每日经济新闻｜米哈游前高管创业，AI原生增长Agent LeapMind Growth获CMC资本领投](https://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2026-04-29/4371679.html)\n[投资界](https://news.pedaily.cn/202604/563315.shtml)\n[36氪](https://eu.36kr.com/zh/p/3786123369094405)",
