      "source": "[OpenAI｜Introducing workspace agents in ChatGPT](https://openai.com/index/introducing-workspace-agents-in-chatgpt/)；[Reuters｜OpenAI brings latest AI models, Codex coding agent to Amazon Bedrock](https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/openai-brings-latest-ai-models-codex-coding-agent-amazon-bedrock-2026-04-28/)",
      "sourceTier": "",
