      "originalText": "We’re introducing an open-source agent orchestrator for deep security reviews. We built it for internal use... Coding agents can now find critical vulnerabilities in minutes... optimized to work with Vercel Sandbox... thousands of agents scrutinizing your codebase in parallel.",
      "originalTranslation": "我们开源了一个用于深度安全评审的 Agent 编排器（DeepSec），最初用于内部；在一些大型开源项目上跑出效果后决定开放。编码 Agent 能在几分钟内发现关键漏洞；结合 Sandbox，可以并行调度大量 Agent 对代码库做安全审计。",
