      "id": "2026-05-03-point-8",
      "slug": "2026-05-03-ai-应用正在从工作工具扩展到生活服务连接器",
      "date": "2026-05-03",
      "rank": 8,
      "title": "AI 应用正在从工作工具扩展到生活服务连接器",
      "person": "Claude Blog",
      "source": "Claude Blog / Connectors",
      "originalUrl": "https://claude.com/blog/connectors-for-everyday-life",
      "originalText": "Starting today, Claude connects to AllTrails, Audible, Booking.com, Instacart, Intuit Credit Karma, Intuit TurboTax, Resy, Spotify, StubHub, Taskrabbit, Thumbtack, Tripadvisor, Uber, Uber Eats, and Viator, with more on the way. Connectors dynamically show up in conversations We’ve also changed how connectors show up in conversations. Claude now suggests the right app for what you’re doing, like finding a reservation, adding to a grocery cart, or identifying a flight. It’s working from what you’ve told it: your preferences, your context, your conversation. This all happens inside your conversation. Ask Claude to recommend a weekend hike, and AllTrails will surface trails nearby that match your preferences. You can then refine the recommendations by asking for something shorter, more scenic, or dog-friendly without leaving the thread. When more than one connected app could help answer your question, Claude shows them all and lets you choose.",
      "originalTranslation": "从今天开始，Claude 可以连接 AllTrails、Audible、Booking.com、Instacart、Intuit Credit Karma、Intuit TurboTax、Resy、Spotify、StubHub、Taskrabbit、Thumbtack、Tripadvisor、Uber、Uber Eats 和 Viator，后续还会支持更多应用。连接器会在对话中动态出现。我们也改变了连接器在对话中出现的方式。Claude 现在会根据你正在做的事情推荐合适的应用，比如查找预订、添加到购物车，或识别航班。它会基于你告诉它的信息来工作：你的偏好、你的上下文、你的对话。所有这些都发生在你的对话内部。你可以让 Claude 推荐一个周末徒步路线，AllTrails 会显示附近符合你偏好的路线。然后你可以继续要求路线更短、更有风景，或者适合带狗，而无需离开这个对话。当不止一个已连接应用可以帮助回答你的问题时，Claude 会全部展示出来，并让你选择。",
      "pointSummary": "Claude 新增一批生活场景连接器，并让连接器根据对话动态出现，覆盖旅行、餐饮、购物、税务、交通等任务。",
      "interpretation": "AI 助手正在从回答问题，转向调度服务和完成任务。",
